---
import MainLayout from '../../layouts/MainLayout.astro';
import Header from '../../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../../components/Footer.astro';
---
<MainLayout title="About me | Lucy Epoxy Studio" description="The story behind Lucy Epoxy Studio." lang="en" pathname="/en/about">
  <Header ctaHref="/en/contact" ctaLabel="Get a quote" />
  <main class="section-sm"><div class="container" style="display:grid;gap:1rem;">
    <img src="/images/about-workshop.jpg" alt="Lucyna at work" class="card" style="width:100%;max-height:520px;object-fit:cover;" />
    <article class="card" style="padding:1.3rem;white-space:pre-line;line-height:1.7;">As a person with a disability, I searched for my place for a long time — not only in the job market, but also in life. Many paths were closed to me, and that is exactly when I discovered craftsmanship, which became my chance, my strength, and a new beginning.

What started as an idea for my own business gradually turned into a true passion. In my work I found myself, meaning, and the joy of creating. I complete every order with heart, care, and gratitude, because I know how much it means to do what you love.

By choosing my services, you support not only a small business, but also a story of determination, courage, and faith that dreams can come true despite obstacles. I invite you to work with me — I create with passion and for people.</article>
    <p class="signature-animate">Lυcуηα Zαωαdzкα-Szpαк</p>
  </div></main>
  <Footer />
  <style>
    .signature-animate {
      font-family: cursive;
      color: #b8954f;
      font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 4vw, 2.4rem);
      transform: rotate(-6deg);
      opacity: .95;
      white-space: nowrap;
      width: 0;
      overflow: hidden;
      border-right: 2px solid rgba(184,149,79,.7);
      animation: sign-write 5.2s steps(28) infinite;
      filter: blur(.35px);
      letter-spacing: .02em;
    }
    @keyframes sign-write {
      0% { width: 0; opacity: 0; }
      8% { opacity: .95; }
      55% { width: 19ch; opacity: .95; }
      75% { width: 19ch; opacity: .95; border-right-color: transparent; }
      100% { width: 0; opacity: 0; border-right-color: rgba(184,149,79,.7); }
    }
  </style>
</MainLayout>
